Harriet Nelson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harriet_Nelson 0 Harriet Nelson (formerly Hilliard; born Peggy Lou Snyder; July 18, 1909 – October 2, 1994) was an American singer and actress. Nelson is best known for her role on the sitcom The Adventures of Ozzie and Harriet.
